  "texts": [
    "To generate service names automatically, we use an LLM.",
    "By inputting user statements into an LLM and commanding it to generate service names, we can obtain a list of automatically generated service names as output.",
    "This process enables the automatic generation of new service names.",
    "The list extracted through string searches in prior research is combined with the list newly generated in this study, forming the final candidate list of service names as the output of Step 1-1.In Step 1-2, as illustrated in Fig. 6, we extract users' needs from their statements while simultaneously identifying specific services.",
    "We instruct the LLM to extract user needs according to the 6W1H framework."
  ],
